  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div xml:id="Aink102-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">
            ituvumatu </p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">
And this is that
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="Aink102">
            <lg type="edition">
              <l> aṉṉai vāḻivēṇ ṭaṉṉai nammūr</l>
              <l> nīṉiṟap peruṅkaṭaṟ puḷḷi ṉāṉātu</l>
                        <l> tuṉpuṟu tuyara nīṅka</l>
                        <l> viṉpuṟa vicaikkumavar tērmaṇik kuralē</l>
                        
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l> Oh mother, please mother </l>
<l> In order for the unending grief that has affliction to abate,</l>
<l> The sound of his chariot’s bells must tinkle joyfully </l>
<l> Like the (call of) birds in our town </l>
<l> (With) the blue-hued big ocean. </l>
            </lg>
        </div>
